    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "@nchmura4 that is a way, but this issue is about filling _before_ reindexing, like `.reindex` provides.\n\ne.g. compare this\n\n```\nIn [9]: s.reindex(pd.date_range(s.index.min(), s.index.max(), freq='D'), fill_value=0).resample('M').sum()\nOut[9]:\n2013-01-31    3\n2013-02-28    0\n2013-03-31    4\nFreq: M, dtype: int64\n\nIn [10]: s.reindex(pd.date_range(s.index.min(), s.index.max(), freq='D'), fill_value=1).resample('M').sum()\nOut[10]:\n2013-01-31    32\n2013-02-28    28\n2013-03-31     4\nFreq: M, dtype: int64\n```\n"
  },
